# Harmony Local Overrides
# This directory contains project-specific overrides for the Harmony framework.
# Files here take precedence over framework defaults.
#
# Structure:
#   local/hooks/       - Override or extend hooks
#   local/agents/      - Override or extend agents
#   local/rules/       - Additional project rules
#   local/patterns/    - Additional project patterns
#
# See: .harmony/docs/overrides.md for documentation
